These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, papaya
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, cain, blend, bolivar
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, scrabble, poker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, drama, satire, thriller
 1. the person watching drama movies is the cain-smoker##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is the blend-smoker##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
 8. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
 9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
10. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
11. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | papaya     | banana   | apple | cucumber |
| Cigar   | cain | montecristo    | bolivar   | blend    |
| Game           | scrabble       | poker   | backgammon   | billiard     |
| Movie-Genre     | drama       | horror | thriller  | satire      |

