.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, tea
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, peas, mango, pomegranate
City: liverpool, miami, venice, berlin
4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, poker, chess
 1. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
 3. the person traveling to berlin is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating pomegranate and the person drinking cola##2
 8. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
 9. the person traveling to miami is the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola       | almond-milk | tea     | iced-tea     |
| Food   | peas      | cranberry       | pomegranate | mango |
| City           | venice       | berlin    | miami     | liverpool         |
| Game     | chess | poker     | bridge     | scrabble       |

