.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, orange, coral, azure
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, martial-arts, satire
City: boston, hannover, liverpool, berlin
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, project-manager, lawyer, photographer
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the photographer is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 3. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
 4. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 5. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the photographer is between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to liverpool##2
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the scientist##1
 8. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the project-manager##5
 9. the scientist is in an even position##4
10. the photographer is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the scientist##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | azure    | coral      | orange   | chestnut |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | martial-arts | horror | satire  |
| City   | hannover   | liverpool         | boston  | berlin  |
| Job           | lawyer      | scientist          | photographer | project-manager  |

