.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-4::.
House: cottage, wooden, craftsman, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, musician, police-officer, writer
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, bus, trike
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, ferret, rabbit
 1. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5
 2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
 4. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 7. the craftsman house is between the person driving the motorbike and the gothic-revival house##2
 8. the musician is on the far left##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
10. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
11. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
12. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
13. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| House      | cottage | wooden     | craftsman        | gothic-revival      |
| Job           | musician    | writer   | police-officer | firefighter |
| Transport   | trike      | motorbike    | jet-ski        | bus         |
| Pet         | chinchilla    | ferret | rabbit         | lizard    |

