 2. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
 3. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
 4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
 5. the person eating plum is the person traveling to hannover##1
 6. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 9. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
10. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
12. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
13. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| City      | venice             | san-francisco       | hannover    | prague       |
