.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, sprite, water
4 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, pony, guinea-pig
4 different games are played: go, monopoly, snooker, billiard
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, board-games, skydiving, card-games
 1. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 3. the person playing go is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person playing billiard##2
 4. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
 9. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Pet          | rabbit    | guinea-pig        | pony     | bird          |
| Game           | monopoly | snooker        | go | billiard |
| Hobby   | card-games    | sudoku     | skydiving      | board-games        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, traveling, puzzles, photography
House: tower, palace, wooden, victorian
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican, british, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 3. the victorian house is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 4. the british is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
 5. the palace house is between the wooden house and the german##2
 6. the british is in an odd position##4
 7. the wooden house is the mexican##1
 8. the british is on the left of the mexican##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the tower house##1
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the british##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby      | puzzles   | photography      | traveling | sudoku     |
| House           | victorian   | tower  | palace        | wooden |
| Nationality   | egyptian     | german     | british      | mexican   |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile | taxi          | roller     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, blend, oliveros, vegafina
House: art-deco, farmhouse, modern, gothic-revival
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike, scooter, roller
 1. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the person driving the roller is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 3. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
 5. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
 7. the modern house is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
 9. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the vegafina-smoker##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Cigar          | tiparillo | oliveros  | vegafina    | blend       |
| House           | farmhouse  | gothic-revival | modern | art-deco  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| Transport   | roller      | scooter    | trike        | snowmobile |

 